下面给你一个“可落地”的前端日志页面组件方案（列表 + 筛选 + 无限滚动/分页 + 详情抽屉 + 自动刷新 + 导出），同时给出接口约定与一个 React 示例。你用 Vue/React/Angular 任何一个都能按这个结构套。

## 1) 页面结构（推荐布局）
- 顶部筛选栏（FilterBar）
  - 时间范围（默认近 15 分钟）
  - 服务/实例（service/host/pod）
  - 环境 env
  - 级别 level（INFO/WARN/ERROR）
  - 关键字 keyword
  - traceId/spanId
  - 仅看异常（hasStack=true）
  - “实时刷新”开关 + 间隔
  - 操作：查询、重置、导出
- 中间日志列表（LogTable / VirtualList）
  - 虚拟滚动（必须）
  - 高亮关键字
  - 行点击展开详情
- 右侧/底部详情（LogDetailDrawer）
  - 原始日志 JSON
  - stacktrace 折叠
  - 复制、查看上下文（前后 N 条）
- 底部状态条
  - 已加载条数、是否还有更多、当前游标、延迟等

## 2) 接口约定（适配大日志量）
### 查询：cursor 分页（不要 offset）
`GET /api/logs?from=...&to=...&service=...&level=...&keyword=...&cursor=...&limit=200`

返回：
```json
{
  "items": [
    {
      "id": "987654321",
      "ts": "2025-12-22T07:02:28.123Z",
      "level": "ERROR",
      "service": "eval",
      "instance": "pod-1",
      "traceId": "abc",
      "logger": "com.xx.Class",
      "thread": "http-nio-8080-exec-1",
      "msg": "something failed",
      "stack": "....(optional)"
    }
  ],
  "nextCursor": "2025-12-22T07:02:28.123Z|987654321",
  "hasMore": true
}
```

### 导出：异步任务
- `POST /api/logs/exports` body=filters -> `{jobId}`
- `GET /api/logs/exports/{jobId}` -> `{status, downloadUrl}`

## 3) 组件拆分（建议）
- `LogPage`：页面容器、URL 参数同步、数据源管理
- `LogFilterBar`：表单（受控），输出 filters
- `useLogDataSource`：核心 hook（请求、防抖、cursor、取消请求、自动刷新）
- `LogVirtualList`：虚拟列表渲染（react-window / react-virtualized / vue-virtual-scroller）
- `LogRow`：一行日志（级别颜色、时间、msg）
- `LogDetailDrawer`：详情展示 + copy + context
- `ExportButton`：触发导出任务、显示进度

## 4) React 示例（Ant Design + react-window）
> 重点：**虚拟列表 + cursor 加载更多 + 自动刷新 + 取消请求**

```tsx
import React, {useEffect, useMemo, useRef, useState} from "react";
import {Button, Drawer, Form, Input, Select, DatePicker, Switch} from "antd";
import {FixedSizeList as List} from "react-window";
import dayjs from "dayjs";

type LogItem = {
  id: string;
  ts: string;
  level: "DEBUG"|"INFO"|"WARN"|"ERROR";
  service?: string;
  instance?: string;
  traceId?: string;
  msg: string;
  stack?: string;
};

type Resp = { items: LogItem[]; nextCursor?: string; hasMore: boolean };

const LEVEL_COLOR: Record<string, string> = {
  DEBUG: "#8c8c8c",
  INFO: "#1677ff",
  WARN: "#faad14",
  ERROR: "#ff4d4f"
};

function buildQuery(params: Record<string, any>) {
  const sp = new URLSearchParams();
  Object.entries(params).forEach(([k, v]) => {
    if (v === undefined || v === null || v === "") return;
    sp.set(k, String(v));
  });
  return sp.toString();
}

async function fetchLogs(filters: any, cursor?: string, signal?: AbortSignal): Promise<Resp> {
  const q = buildQuery({...filters, cursor, limit: 200});
  const r = await fetch(`/api/logs?${q}`, {signal});
  if (!r.ok) throw new Error(await r.text());
  return r.json();
}

export default function LogPage() {
  const [form] = Form.useForm();

  const [items, setItems] = useState<LogItem[]>([]);
  const [cursor, setCursor] = useState<string|undefined>(undefined);
  const [hasMore, setHasMore] = useState(true);
  const [loading, setLoading] = useState(false);

  const [selected, setSelected] = useState<LogItem|null>(null);

  const [autoRefresh, setAutoRefresh] = useState(false);
  const abortRef = useRef<AbortController | null>(null);

  const filters = Form.useWatch([], form);

  const normalizedFilters = useMemo(() => {
    // 把 RangePicker 的值转成 ISO
    const [from, to] = filters?.range ?? [];
    return {
      service: filters?.service,
      level: filters?.level,
      keyword: filters?.keyword,
      traceId: filters?.traceId,
      from: from ? dayjs(from).toISOString() : undefined,
      to: to ? dayjs(to).toISOString() : undefined
    };
  }, [filters]);

  const load = async (mode: "reset"|"more" = "more") => {
    if (loading) return;
    setLoading(true);

    // 取消上一个请求，防止并发/抖动
    abortRef.current?.abort();
    const ac = new AbortController();
    abortRef.current = ac;

    try {
      const next = await fetchLogs(normalizedFilters, mode === "reset" ? undefined : cursor, ac.signal);
      setItems(prev => mode === "reset" ? next.items : [...prev, ...next.items]);
      setCursor(next.nextCursor);
      setHasMore(next.hasMore);
    } finally {
      setLoading(false);
    }
  };

  // 初始值
  useEffect(() => {
    form.setFieldsValue({
      range: [dayjs().subtract(15, "minute"), dayjs()],
      level: undefined
    });
  }, []);

  // filters 变化：重置加载（建议加防抖，这里省略）
  useEffect(() => {
    if (!normalizedFilters?.from || !normalizedFilters?.to) return;
    setItems([]);
    setCursor(undefined);
    setHasMore(true);
    load("reset");
  }, [normalizedFilters.service, normalizedFilters.level, normalizedFilters.keyword, normalizedFilters.traceId, normalizedFilters.from, normalizedFilters.to]);

  // 自动刷新：只刷新“最新”窗口（重置模式）
  useEffect(() => {
    if (!autoRefresh) return;
    const t = setInterval(() => {
      load("reset");
    }, 3000);
    return () => clearInterval(t);
  }, [autoRefresh, normalizedFilters, cursor]);

  const Row = ({index, style}: any) => {
    const it = items[index];
    return (
      <div
        style={{...style, display:"flex", gap:12, padding:"0 12px", cursor:"pointer", borderBottom:"1px solid #f0f0f0"}}
        onClick={() => setSelected(it)}
        title={it.msg}
      >
        <div style={{width: 210, color:"#595959"}}>{dayjs(it.ts).format("YYYY-MM-DD HH:mm:ss.SSS")}</div>
        <div style={{width: 80, color: LEVEL_COLOR[it.level]}}>{it.level}</div>
        <div style={{width: 140, color:"#262626"}}>{it.service}</div>
        <div style={{flex: 1, whiteSpace:"nowrap", overflow:"hidden", textOverflow:"ellipsis"}}>{it.msg}</div>
      </div>
    );
  };

  return (
    <div style={{padding: 12}}>
      <Form form={form} layout="inline">
        <Form.Item name="range" label="时间">
          <DatePicker.RangePicker showTime />
        </Form.Item>
        <Form.Item name="service" label="服务">
          <Input style={{width: 160}} placeholder="service" />
        </Form.Item>
        <Form.Item name="level" label="级别">
          <Select allowClear style={{width: 120}}
            options={["DEBUG","INFO","WARN","ERROR"].map(v => ({value:v, label:v}))} />
        </Form.Item>
        <Form.Item name="keyword" label="关键字">
          <Input style={{width: 200}} placeholder="error/timeout..." />
        </Form.Item>
        <Form.Item name="traceId" label="traceId">
          <Input style={{width: 200}} />
